Johnathan Paul WEBER, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
DEPARTMENT OF REVENUE, O/B/O Kirstie Lee HORNE, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D17-4820 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. January 25, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:
